<p><supplied reason="subaudible"><quote type="basetext" xml:lang="san-Latn">
	<lg met="anuṣṭubh">
	<l>vyavahārān didr̥kṣus tu brāhmaṇaiḥ saha pārthivaḥ</l>
	<l>mantrajñair mantribhiś caiva vinītaḥ praviśet sabhām ||</l>
	</lg>
   <note type="parallels">
