	<lg met="anuṣṭubh">
	<l>hiṁsāṁ yaḥ kurute kaś cid deyaṁ vā na prayacchati |</l>
	<l>sthāne te dve vivādasya bhinno ’ṣṭādaśadhā punaḥ ||</l>
	</lg><note type="parallels">
         <list>
          <item>This stanza is absent from <bibl><ptr target="bibl:Olivelle2005_01"/>Olivelle</bibl>'s constituted text, though it is referenced in his app. crit. for one manuscript. The stanza occurs in ed. <bibl><ptr target="bibl:Mandlik1886_01"/>Mandlik</bibl> 8.4 with reading <foreign>bhinno</foreign>, where the Svayambhu implies <foreign>bhinne</foreign>.</item>
